tle=Demonetisation could lead to long-pending electoral reforms|date=2016-11-11|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205746/https://www.hindustantimes.com/analysis/demonetisation-could-lead-to-long-pending-electoral-reforms/story-tXYgT7hw6Q3TQUbPuIUucO.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度社会活动家[[安纳·哈扎尔|安纳·哈扎尔]]称，废止是一个革命性的一步<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/anna-hazare-hails-demonetisation-calls-it-revolutionary-step/articleshow/55354898.cms|title=Anna Hazare hails demonetisation, calls it 'revolutionary' step|work=The Economic Times|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205729/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/anna-hazare-hails-demonetisation-calls-it-revolutionary-step/articleshow/55354898.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/demonitisation-a-revolutionary-step-to-fight-corruption-anna-hazare-4367070/|title=Demonetisation a revolutionary step to fight corruption: Anna Hazare|date=2016-11-10|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205824/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/demonitisation-a-revolutionary-step-to-fight-corruption-anna-hazare-4367070/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ndtv.com/india-news/notes-ban-anna-hazare-hails-pm-narendra-modis-revolutionary-step-kejriwal-criticizes-it-1623922|title=Notes Ban: Anna Hazare Hails PM Narendra Modi's 'Revolutionary' Step, Kejriwal Criticizes It|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130113402/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/notes-ban-anna-hazare-hails-pm-narendra-modis-revolutionary-step-kejriwal-criticizes-it-1623922|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度总统[[普拉纳布·慕克吉|普拉纳布·慕克吉]]对通过以果决行动对废钞表达欢迎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/india/president-pranab-mukherjee-welcomes-demonetisation-of-rs-1000-and-rs-500-notes_1947632.html|title=President Pranab Mukherjee welcomes demonetisation of Rs 1,000 and Rs 500 notes|date=2016-11-08|publisher=india.com|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205814/https://zeenews.india.com/news/india/president-pranab-mukherjee-welcomes-demonetisation-of-rs-1000-and-rs-500-notes_1947632.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/demonetisation-of-rs-1000-and-rs-500-notes-bold-step-president-pranab-mukherjee-4364815/|title=Demonetisation of Rs 1,000 and Rs 500 notes bold step: President Pranab Mukherjee|date=2016-11-08|work=The Indian Express|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205821/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/india-news-india/demonetisation-of-rs-1000-and-rs-500-notes-bold-step-president-pranab-mukherjee-4364815/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ndtv.com/india-news/president-pranab-mukherjee-welcomes-demonetisation-of-rs-1-000-rs-500-notes-1623081|title=President Pranab Mukherjee Welcomes Demonetisation of Rs 1,000, Rs 500 Notes|publisher=ndtv.com|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205803/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/president-pranab-mukherjee-welcomes-demonetisation-of-rs-1-000-rs-500-notes-1623081|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/demonetisation-of-rs-500-rs-1000-notes-a-bold-step-says-pranab-mukherjee/article9320915.ece|title=A bold step, says Pranab Mukherjee|date=2016-11-09|work=The Hindu|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2016-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126175651/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/demonetisation-of-rs-500-rs-1000-notes-a-bold-step-says-pranab-mukherjee/article9320915.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在社交网站上，民众的反应都有所不同<ref name="ToI Twitter reaction">{{cite news|url=http://blogs.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/everything-social/rs-500-1000-notes-pulled-out-how-twitter-reacted/|title=Rs 500, 1000 notes pulled out: How Twitter reacted|date=8 November 2016|work=Times of India Blogs|accessdate=8 November 2016|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627220316/https://blogs.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/everything-social/rs-500-1000-notes-pulled-out-how-twitter-reacted/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般来说废止和试图阻止洗黑钱的行动受到了赞赏，但是，一些普通人对此方式受到了批评，原因是会对日常生活造成困苦<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloombergquint.com/opinion/2016/11/11/dear-pm-modi-demonetisation-brahmastra-could-have-spared-the-poor|title=Dear PM Modi, Demonetisation 'Brahmastra' Could Have Spared The Poor|date=8 November 2016|publisher=Bloomberg Quint|author=Raghav Bahl|accessdate=2016-11-12|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205813/https://www.bloombergquint.com/opinion/2016/11/11/dear-pm-modi-demonetisation-brahmastra-could-have-spared-the-poor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

