中国媒体《[[环球时报|环球时报]]》的一篇专栏文章称赞该计划是“大胆而果断地打击黑钱和腐败”，并称印度还需结构性改革以根治腐败<ref name="Chinese state media">{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/china-state-media-praises-modi-but-says-he/article9343797.ece|title=State media praises Modi, but says he can learn from China's crusade against corruption|first=Atul|last=Aneja|date=14 November 2016|work=The Hindu|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2016-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114093339/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/china-state-media-praises-modi-but-says-he/article9343797.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。芬兰前首相和[[欧盟委员会|欧盟委员会]]副主席[[于尔基·卡泰宁|于尔基·卡泰宁]]对废止计划表示欢迎，强调提高透明度，以加强印度经济发展<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/indias-crackdown-on-black-money-to-help-financial-system-eu/articleshow/55399290.cms|title=European Union welcomes India's step on demonetisation|work=The Economic Times|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091514/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/indias-crackdown-on-black-money-to-help-financial-system-eu/articleshow/55399290.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news18.com/news/business/indias-crackdown-on-black-money-will-help-financial-system-european-union-1311545.html|title=India's Crackdown on Black Money Will Help Financial System: European Union|date=2016-11-13|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105205842/https://www.news18.com/news/business/indias-crackdown-on-black-money-will-help-financial-system-european-union-1311545.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]南亚通讯员{{le|贾斯丁·洛拉特|Justin Rowlatt}}在他的文章中称赞了其保密性和成功的原因<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-37974423|title=Why India wiped out 86% of its cash overnight|first=Justin|last=Rowlatt|date=2016-11-14|work=bbc.com|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215235907/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-37974423|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英国作家{{le|蒂姆·沃斯特尔|Tim Worstall}}在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志上发表文章，将这一计划称之为宏观经济效应<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/timworstall/2016/11/17/indias-rs-500-and-1000-demonetisation-is-lowering-interest-rates-and-also-inflation/#62464fde2edf|title=India's Rs 500 And 1,000 Demonetization Is Lowering Interest Rates And Also Inflation|first=Tim|last=Worstall|publisher=|accessdate=2016-11-24|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125123520/https://www.forbes.com/sites/timworstall/2016/11/17/indias-rs-500-and-1000-demonetisation-is-lowering-interest-rates-and-also-inflation/#62464fde2edf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新加坡报纸《独立报》发表了一篇题为《莫迪模仿李光耀根治印度腐败》的评论<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://theindependent.sg/modi-does-a-lee-kuan-yew-to-stamp-out-corruption-in-india/|title=Modi does a Lee Kuan Yew to stamp out corruption in India|date=2016-11-10|newspaper=The Independent|access-date=2016-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103923/https://theindependent.sg/modi-does-a-lee-kuan-yew-to-stamp-out-corruption-in-india/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===反对意见===
2016年11月8日，西孟加拉邦首席部长{{le|马马塔·班纳吉|Mamata Banerjee}}称，这一计划是一个“悲剧”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/demonitisation-of-rs500-and-rs-1000-currency-notes-reactions/article9320639.ece | title=Demonetisation of Rs. 500 and Rs. 1000: Who says what | work=The Hindu | date=2016-11-08 | accessdate=2016-11-09 | archive-date=2016-11-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119085628/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/demonitisation-of-rs500-and-rs-1000-currency-notes-reactions/article9320639.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|印度国家联盟|Indian National League}}总书记塞尼·艾哈迈德，也向马德拉斯高等法院提交了一项公共利益诉讼（PIL），以废除该决定。但[[印度高等法院|印度高等法院]]驳回了诉讼，称它不能干预政府的货币政策<ref>{{cite web |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/articleshow/55353472.cms?utm_source=contentofinterest&utm_medium=text&utm_campaign=cppst |title=Govt's demonetisation move fit for country's security, development: HC |work=The Economic Times |date=2016-11-10 |accessdate=2016-11-10 |archive-date=2019-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810112309/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/articleshow/55353472.cms?utm_source=contentofinterest&utm_medium=text&utm_campaign=cppst |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印度高等法院也曾收到过类似的公共利益诉讼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/pils-supreme-court-rs-500-rs-1000-notes-illegal/1/807124.html |title=PILs in Supreme Court against making Rs 500, Rs 1000 notes illegal |work=India Today |date=2016-11-10 |accessdate=2016-11-10 |archive-date=2017-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226073312/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/pils-supreme-court-rs-500-rs-1000-notes-illegal/1/807124.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但尚未就此事作出决定，预计会在2016年12月2日听证。前[[世界银行|世界银行]]首席经济学家{{le|卡西克·巴苏|Kaushik Basu}}表示，“损害”可能比任何可能的好处大得多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/economy-policy/demonetisation-damage-greater-than-its-benefits-says-kaushik-basu-116111101733_1.html |title=Demonetisation damage greater than its benefits, says Kaushik Basu |work=Business Standard |date=2016-11-12 |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929212009/https://www.business-standard.com/article/economy-policy/demonetisation-damage-greater-than-its-benefits-says-kaushik-basu-116111101733_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=PTI |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/gst-good-economics-demonetisation-is-not-kaushik-basu/articleshow/55375545.cms |title=GST good economics; demonetisation is not: Kaushik Basu |work=The Economic Times |date=2016-11-11 |accessdate=2016-11-12 |archive-date=2019-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818052448/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/gst-good-economics-demonetisation-is-not-kaushik-basu/articleshow/55375545.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

曾任[[贾瓦哈拉尔·尼赫鲁大学|贾瓦哈拉尔·尼赫鲁大学]]经济学教授的{{le|普拉哈特·帕特奈克|Prabhat Patnaik}}称，此次废止“无情”、“反人民”。他也批评洗黑钱被假定为“现金囤积”的简单方法，对消除“黑人活动”没有影响，而且会“给普通人造成很大的困难”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Patnaik|first1=Prabhat|title=Demonetization: Witless and Anti-People|url=http://www.thecitizen.in/index.php/NewsDetail/index/1/9151/Demonetization-Witless-and-Anti-People|accessdate=13 November 2016|work=The Citizen|date=2016-11-09|archive-date=2017-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171101220138/http://www.thecitizen.in/index.php/NewsDetail/index/1/9151/Demonetization-Witless-and-Anti-People|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由印度国会牵头的包括13个政党的反对党，在2016年11月16日的议会冬季会议上表示，反对现任政府的大面额纸币废止问题。西孟加拉邦首席部长{{le|马马塔·班纳吉|Mamata Banerjee}}也会见了印度总统[[普拉纳布·慕克吉|普拉纳布·慕克吉]]，反对这一废止计划<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-demonetization-debate-likely-to-hot-up-winter-session-didi-to-knock-on-president-s-door-2273770|title=Debate on demonetisation, in winter session|work=DNA India.com|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210004/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-demonetization-debate-likely-to-hot-up-winter-session-didi-to-knock-on-president-s-door-2273770|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Demonetisation-People-battle-it-out-at-banks-netas-ready-for-war-in-Parliament/articleshow/55424673.cms|title=Winter Session debate|work=The Times of India|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2019-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818052451/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Demonetisation-People-battle-it-out-at-banks-netas-ready-for-war-in-Parliament/articleshow/55424673.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/winter-session-oppn-to-target-govt-on-demonetisation-orop-gst-116111401558_1.html|title=Opposition to target government on demonetisation|work=Business Standard|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126143810/http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/winter-session-oppn-to-target-govt-on-demonetisation-orop-gst-116111401558_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/live-november-15-2016-effect-of-demonetisation-of-rs-500-rs-1000-notes/article9348006.ece|title=Government and Opposition prepare for winter session of Parliament, on demonetisation|work=The Hindu|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2016-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127042520/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/live-november-15-2016-effect-of-demonetisation-of-rs-500-rs-1000-notes/article9348006.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/india/demonetisation-janata-dal-u-gives-suspension-of-business-notice-as-parties-gear-up-for-war-in-parliament_1949763.html|title=Parties gear up for debate on demonetisation|work=zeenews.India.com|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210033/https://zeenews.india.com/news/india/demonetisation-janata-dal-u-gives-suspension-of-business-notice-as-parties-gear-up-for-war-in-parliament_1949763.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/opposition-parties-agree-to-raise-notes-issue-in-session/articleshow/55424453.cms|title=Parties agree to raise notes issue in session|work=The Economic Times|date=2016-11-15|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210000/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/opposition-parties-agree-to-raise-notes-issue-in-session/articleshow/55424453.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。关于反对废止的辩论是由印度国民大会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/india/live-parliament-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-demonetization-congress-bjp-tmc-rahul-mamata-modi-sena-black-money-banks-atms-2273883|title=Congress on demonetisation|work=DNA India|date=2016-11-16|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130154733/https://www.dnaindia.com/india/live-parliament-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-demonetization-congress-bjp-tmc-rahul-mamata-modi-sena-black-money-banks-atms-2273883|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{le|安纳德·沙玛|Anand Sharma}}在2016年11月16日发起的<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.financialexpress.com/india-news/url-live-winter-session-of-parliament-begins-today-narendra-modi-speech-rahul-gandhi-arun-jaitley-demonetisation-effects/446936/|title= Anand Sharma speaks on demonetisation|work= The Financial Express|date= 2016-11-16|access-date= 2016-11-28|archive-date= 2019-11-28|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191128191420/https://www.financialexpress.com/india-news/url-live-winter-session-of-parliament-begins-today-narendra-modi-speech-rahul-gandhi-arun-jaitley-demonetisation-effects/446936/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://zeenews.india.com/live-updates/parliament-debate-on-demonetisation-1950128|title=Congress initiates demonetisation debate|work=Zeenews.India.com|date=2016-11-16|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210044/https://zeenews.india.com/live-updates/parliament-debate-on-demonetisation-1950128|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而马马塔·班纳吉被认为是第一个反对莫迪政府废止大面额纸币的计划<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/Whys-Didi-against-demonetisation/articleshow/55378644.cms|title=Why's Mamata Banerjee against demonetization?|work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|date=2016-11-12|access-date=2016-11-28|archive-date=2019-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818130113/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/Whys-Didi-against-demonetisation/articleshow/55378644.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2016年11月17日和18日[[联邦院_(印度)|印度联邦院]]第二和第三天的辩论中，反对派和莫迪政府支持派在争论议题上发生冲突，使议会遭到停会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/winter-session-of-parliament-parliament-proceedings-november-18-2016/article9360240.ece|title=As it happened: RS, LS adjourned till Monday|publisher=The Hindu|accessdate=2016-11-18|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122000148/http://www.thehindu.com/news/winter-session-of-parliament-parliament-proceedings-november-18-2016/article9360240.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年11月24日，在[[联邦院_(印度)|印度联邦院]]的前议会辩论中，印度前总理[[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]表示：“这个计划会伤害小行业和农业部门。由于这一举动，GDP可能下降约3％”，同时表示这是“历史性决策失误”。而他还质疑“我想问总理一下，有没有一些国家的人们把钱存入银行，不允许自己取钱的的例子。 ”他后来又说：“银行每天都会发出新的通知，这是不好的，因为它没有在总理办公室，财政部长和印度储备银行适当地反映。合作银行系统已被阻止处理现金<ref>{{cite web | url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/is-modi-proving-manmohan-singh-right-with-slew-of-u-turns-on-cash-ban/articleshow/55632062.cms | title=Is Modi proving Manmohan Singh right with slew of U-turns on cash ban? | access-date=2016-11-28 | archive-date=2021-01-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210035/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/is-modi-proving-manmohan-singh-right-with-slew-of-u-turns-on-cash-ban/articleshow/55632062.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://money.163.com/16/1125/00/C6M6CD58002580S6.html|title=印度前总理辛格炮轰"废钞"：这是历史性决策失误|publisher=第一财经日报(上海)|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126152335/http://money.163.com/16/1125/00/C6M6CD58002580S6.html|archive-date=2016-11-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>”。同日，一些大面额纸币废止计划反对者也上街游行，抗议莫迪废除500及1000卢比的决议，与警察发生冲突<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cri.cn/20161125/c278a905-ccfc-b80d-27ef-158ddfe5b135.html|title=印度民众连日抗议废除高额卢比 与警察发生冲突|publisher=国际在线|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801233151/http://news.cri.cn/20161125/c278a905-ccfc-b80d-27ef-158ddfe5b135.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月28日，印度多個城市再有民眾上街示威，继续就政府突然宣布废止大面额钞票的计划表示抗议。反对派也要求總理莫迪向國會解釋原因，又警告措施可能會引發暴動<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=202021|title=印度多處示威抗議廢除大面額鈔票|publisher=now新闻|accessdate=2016-11-29|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105210050/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=202021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而[[尼泊尔中央银行|尼泊尔中央银行]]也发布命令，禁止使用印度新版500及2000卢比面值钞票，并认定上述两种钞票是“未经授权及非法的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2016-11-25/doc-ifxyawxa2733375.shtml|title=尼泊尔禁止使用印度新版500及2000卢比面值钞票|publisher=中国新闻网|accessdate=2016-11-25|archive-date=2019-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810130905/http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2016-11-25/doc-ifxyawxa2733375.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

